<body>
Reports the following JPA specification errors:
<ul>
  <li>Several attributes are configured for a method or field</li>
  <li>Illegal attribute is used in Embeddable object (JPA 1.0)</li>
  <li>Persistent attribute metadata is specified not on a field or property getter</li>
  <li>No setter or getter with property-based access</li>
</ul>

<p><b>Example:</b></p>
<pre><code lang="java">
  @Entity
  @Table(name = "TABLE")
  public class JavaEntity {

    private Integer id; // Error: both getter and setter should be present

    public Integer getId() { ... }



    private String data;

    public String getData() { ... }

    @Basic // Error: persistence annotation should be placed on field or getter method
    public void setData(String data) { ... }
  }
</code></pre><br/>
</body>
